            // This is the Maximum Weight Independent Set problem on a Cycle Graph (which is equivalent to finding minimum cost selection of k items with distance constraints).
            // We solve this using DP on a path graph (linear) twice (once fixing node 0 in, once fixing node 0 out).

            // 1. Solve for the path graph 0..N-1 (linear DP)
